{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4d94de5cc8","title":"陈伯达对北京外语学院造反团冲外交部一事的电话指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"173c208ade","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":26,"articleId":"4d94de5cc8"}],"tags":[{"id":"2bffb53b5b","name":"对外关系和政策","type":"主题"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c1ca4966eb","type":"title","text":"陈伯达对北京外语学院造反团冲外交部一事的电话指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4d94de5cc8"},{"id":"2242f3b5a5","type":"paragraph","text":"〖26日晚，北外红旗大队经总理批准在人大会堂斗批陈毅，此时北外造反团地院等冲击了外交部。陈伯达同志26日晚对北外造反团冲击外交部一事作了三点指示。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4d94de5cc8"},{"id":"48ae88ede8","type":"paragraph","text":"一、冲击外交部是错误的，冲击今天的批陈是错误的。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4d94de5cc8"},{"id":"d4d077f29c","type":"paragraph","text":"二、今天揪陈毅是错误的。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4d94de5cc8"},{"id":"bf56e571d1","type":"paragraph","text":"三、立即撤出外交部。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4d94de5cc8"}],"page":{"id":"364507d45d","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"4d94de5cc8","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}